{"slug":"games","title":"games","date":"2021-07-16","excerpt":"TODO","tags":["todo"],"html":"<p>I’ve made a few web games in recently. I’ll try to keep this page updated as I make more.</p>\n<h2 id=\"empire\">Empire<a aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\" href=\"#empire\"><span class=\"heading-link\">#</span></a></h2>\n<picture class=\"svelte-1gy5t1o\"><source srcset=\"/optimized-images/posts/games/emipre.avif\" type=\"image/avif\">\n\t<source srcset=\"/optimized-images/posts/games/emipre.webp\" type=\"image/webp\">\n\t<img src=\"/optimized-images/posts/games/emipre.png\" alt=\"Empire Lobby\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"svelte-1gy5t1o\">\n\t\n\t\t<figcaption><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->Empire Lobby<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></figcaption>\n</picture>\n<p><a href=\"https://empire.ihtfy.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">PLAY</a></p>\n<p>Based on the party game. I should make a full post about this one.</p>\n<p>I tried a lot of new things while making this game; this was my first multiplayer game.</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"telewave\">Telewave<a aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\" href=\"#telewave\"><span class=\"heading-link\">#</span></a></h2>\n<picture class=\"svelte-1gy5t1o\"><source srcset=\"/optimized-images/posts/games/telewave-2.avif\" type=\"image/avif\">\n\t<source srcset=\"/optimized-images/posts/games/telewave-2.webp\" type=\"image/webp\">\n\t<img src=\"/optimized-images/posts/games/telewave-2.png\" alt=\"Telewave\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"svelte-1gy5t1o\">\n\t\n\t\t<figcaption><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->Telewave<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></figcaption>\n</picture>\n<p><a href=\"https://telewave.ihtfy.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">PLAY</a></p>\n<p>Based on the board game, <a href=\"https://www.wavelength.zone/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Wavelength</a>.</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"optics\">Optics<a aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\" href=\"#optics\"><span class=\"heading-link\">#</span></a></h2>\n<picture class=\"svelte-1gy5t1o\"><source srcset=\"/optimized-images/posts/games/optics.avif\" type=\"image/avif\">\n\t<source srcset=\"/optimized-images/posts/games/optics.webp\" type=\"image/webp\">\n\t<img src=\"/optimized-images/posts/games/optics.png\" alt=\"Optics\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"svelte-1gy5t1o\">\n\t\n\t\t<figcaption><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->Optics<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></figcaption>\n</picture>\n<p><a href=\"https://optics.ihtfy.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">PLAY</a></p>\n<p>Based on the card game, <a href=\"https://pandasaurusgames.com/products/illusion\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Illusion</a>. I first played this over the 4th of July weekend.</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"knight-puzzle\">Knight Puzzle<a aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\" href=\"#knight-puzzle\"><span class=\"heading-link\">#</span></a></h2>\n<picture class=\"svelte-1gy5t1o\"><source srcset=\"/optimized-images/posts/games/knight.avif\" type=\"image/avif\">\n\t<source srcset=\"/optimized-images/posts/games/knight.webp\" type=\"image/webp\">\n\t<img src=\"/optimized-images/posts/games/knight.png\" alt=\"Knight Puzzle\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"svelte-1gy5t1o\">\n\t\n\t\t<figcaption><!-- HTML_TAG_START -->Knight Puzzle<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></figcaption>\n</picture>\n<p><a href=\"https://knightpuzzle.ihtfy.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">PLAY</a></p>\n<p>I have some details in <a href=\"https://site.ihtfy.com/knight/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">this post</a>. This is a chess puzzle where you have to move the knight around the board without being attacked by the queen.</p>","css":{"code":"picture.svelte-1gy5t1o.svelte-1gy5t1o{position:relative;width:100%;height:100%}picture.svelte-1gy5t1o img.svelte-1gy5t1o{width:100%;height:100%}","map":null},"head":"","readingTime":"2 min read","relatedPosts":[{"slug":"habit","title":"habit","date":"2022-04-02","excerpt":"TODO","tags":["todo"],"html":"<p>I still get reminders from the WordPress app to post everyday. Some days it doesn’t work though.</p>\n<p>I started working on building my website with sveltekit again. It’s at <a href=\"https://site.ihtfy.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">site.ihtfy.com</a> for now, but eventually I’ll put it on <a href=\"https://ihtfy.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">ihtfy.com</a> and <a href=\"https://frankiemercado.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">frankiemercado.com</a> will forward to <a href=\"https://ihtfy.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">ihtfy.com</a> I think.</p>","css":{"code":"","map":null},"head":"","readingTime":"1 min read"},{"slug":"again","title":"again","date":"2022-03-31","excerpt":"TODO","tags":["todo"],"html":"<p>I forgot to write again.</p>","css":{"code":"","map":null},"head":"","readingTime":"1 min read"},{"slug":"wombo","title":"wombo","date":"2022-03-31","excerpt":"TODO","tags":["todo"],"html":"<p>I’ve been using <a href=\"https://app.wombo.art/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">this site</a> to make the thumbnail images for these posts - using the title as the prompt.</p>\n<p>The last two days, I forgot to write until just after midnight. I adjusted the post date to be 11:59pm just to keep the dates consistent, but I failed to adhere to the original goal. I think I will move to the weekly posts, and just update the draft throughout the week. This should mean there are no more totally junk posts like the last two days.</p>\n<p>Once I migrate to my new site - by June 21, 2022 - I may consolidate these last 3 months of daily posts.</p>","css":{"code":"","map":null},"head":"","readingTime":"1 min read"}]}